<i>noun</i>: 허탈감 [허탈감], 실의 [시릐/시리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허탈감 [허탈감]</dt><br>
<dd>spiritlessness; dejection; despondency</dd><br>
<dd>몸의 기운이 빠지고 정신이 멍한 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling that one is losing one's energy and becoming absent-minded.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>실의 [시릐/시리]</dt><br>
<dd>disappointment; despair; dejection</dd><br>
<dd>뜻이나 의욕을 잃음.</dd><br>
<dd>Loss of a will or motivation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>